OL,6,FA woman has denied plotting with her
OL,7,Fsecret lover to murder her husband so
OL,8,Fthey could start a new life together,
OL,9,Fa court has heard.
OL,11,FEthel Mills, 46, known as Michelle, is
OL,12,Fstanding trial alongside Geraint
OL,13,FBerry, 46, and Steven Thomas, 47,
OL,14,Faccused of conspiring to kill
OL,15,FChristopher Mills.
