OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,FMr Mills was attacked at a static
OL,7,Fcaravan he shared with his wife in
OL,8,FSeptember 2024 by two masked
OL,9,Fintruders, bearing imitation handguns
OL,10,Fand carrying gas masks, pliers and
OL,11,Fcable ties in a rucksack.
OL,13,FSwansea Crown Court heard Berry, an ex-
OL,14,Fmarine who is alleged to have been one
OL,15,Fof the attackers, had been engaged in
OL,16,Fa secret relationship with Mills for
OL,17,Faround three months leading up to the
OL,18,Fassault and had shared his fantasies
OL,19,Fwith Mills about killing her husband.
