OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,FMills and her husband, also ex-forces,
OL,7,Fmarried in 2018 and lived together at
OL,8,FMaes Ty Gwyn, Llangennech, in Swansea,
OL,9,Fbut the attack took place at a static
OL,10,Fcaravan they shared in Cenarth,
OL,11,FCarmarthenshire.
OL,13,FWhile Mr Mills was not aware of any
OL,14,Fproblems with their relationship, his
OL,15,Fwife was said to have begun an affair
OL,16,Fwith Berry in June 2024.
