OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,FJonathan Rees KC, prosecuting, said:
OL,7,F"Michelle Mills and Geraint Berry had
OL,8,Fembarked on a secret sexual
OL,9,Frelationship which, on Geraint Berry's
OL,10,Fpart at least, had become increasingly
OL,11,Fintense.
OL,13,F"In that short period of time, Berry,
OL,14,Fencouraged on by Michelle Mills, had
OL,15,Fbecome increasingly occupied by
OL,16,Fhostile thoughts about Christopher
OL,17,FMills."
