OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,FThe court heard excerpts from text
OL,7,Fmessages between Mills and Berry in
OL,8,Fthe weeks leading up to the attack, in
OL,9,Fwhich he fantasised that her husband
OL,10,Fshould "just die" and urged her to
OL,11,Fsmother him with a pillow or poison
OL,12,Fhim by putting antifreeze in his gravy.
OL,14,FMr Rees added: "The only concern that
OL,15,FMichelle Mills showed throughout was
OL,16,Fto ensure that she and Geraint Berry
OL,17,Fcould get away with it."
