OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,FOn the night of September 20 2024, Mr
OL,7,FMills and his wife were sitting in the
OL,8,Fliving room of the caravan when he
OL,9,Fanswered a knock at the door.
OL,11,FHe was met by two masked men armed
OL,12,Fwith guns, who proceeded to enter the
OL,13,Fcaravan and launch an assault on him,
OL,14,Fstriking him in the face. Mr Mills
OL,15,Ffought off his attackers, who fled the
OL,16,Fscene.
