OL,6,F"The police attended shortly
OL,7,Fafterwards, and the two intruders,
OL,8,FGeraint Berry and Steven Thomas, were
OL,9,Fdiscovered hiding in undergrowth near
OL,10,Fto the caravan site," Mr Rees said.
OL,12,FOne of the men was found to be
OL,13,Fcarrying a forged suicide note,
OL,14,Fpurporting to be written by Mr Mills
OL,15,Fand addressed to his wife.
