OL,3,CWife denies plotting with secret lover
OL,4,Cto murder husband
OL,6,F"The prosecution says the truth is
OL,7,Fthat Geraint Berry, Michelle Mills and
OL,8,FSteven Thomas agreed to unlawfully
OL,9,Fkill Christopher Mills ` to murder him
OL,10,F` and that their communications and
OL,11,Ftheir actions demonstrate that they
OL,12,Fwere both persistent and deadly
OL,13,Fserious about it," Mr Rees added.
OL,15,FBerry, of Clydach, Swansea, and
OL,16,FThomas, of Blaengwynfi, in the Afan
OL,17,FValley, have admitted to possessing an
OL,18,Fimitation firearm but pleaded not
OL,19,Fguilty to conspiracy to murder.
